DataSource.query:
Select Fiscal_Week_Num_RMS as FiscalWeek, LocationID, Count(Distinct OrderNumber) as NumberOrdersÂ 
from CMS2000.dbo.BOHKioskTransactions O with (nolock) join CMS2000.dbo.TimeDimension T with (nolock)
on T.Phys_Date = O.DrawerDate
where DrawerDate between '09/29/14' and '09/27/15' and LocationID > 99
group by Fiscal_Week_Num_RMS, LocationID
order by Fiscal_Week_Num_RMS, LocationID
